<http://www.spektrix.com/thecultch/event/126001ACMCHQKLPGTVRJNMSSRRJRCJGVB> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "In Conversation: Before the Show";
  schema:description """
	<h1> In Conversation: Before the Show</h1><h2>Presented by The Search Party</h2>Founders Lounge in the Historic Theatre<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This panel, presented in connection with People, Places & Things, is an open conversation about addiction and rehabilitation. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guided by the host and joined by invited panelists, the discussion will draw from lived experience and reflection to explore the realities and complexities of recovery, with time reserved for audience questions and dialogue.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Book your complimentary seat now.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">While there’s no cost to attend, donations are gratefully accepted for those who feel moved to contribute. In-person donations can be made by debit, credit card, or cash. All proceeds will support Westminster House’s Aboriginal programming.</span>
""";
